---
// Cyprus FAQ Section
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 bg-background">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-[42px] font-bold font-serif text-secondary mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground">Everything you need to know about getting married in Cyprus</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <details class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6 group">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
          <h3 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-secondary">What is the best time of year to get married in Cyprus?</h3>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4 leading-relaxed">The most popular months are between May and October when the weather is consistently warm and sunny. July and August can be very hot, so many couples prefer the slightly milder temperatures of late spring or early autumn.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6 group">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
          <h3 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-secondary">What are the legal requirements for a wedding in Cyprus?</h3>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4 leading-relaxed">Cyprus is one of the easiest destinations for UK couples. You'll need to be in the country for at least 3 business days before your ceremony. Requirements include valid passports, birth certificates, and certificates of no impediment (CNI).</p>
      </details>

      <details class="bg-surface rounded-xl p-6 group">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
          <h3 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-secondary">How far in advance should we book our Cyprus wedding?</h3>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </summary>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4 leading-relaxed">We recommend booking 18-24 months in advance to secure your preferred date and venue, especially for popular Saturday dates. However, we can often arrange weddings with shorter lead times depending on availability.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>